- **Incorporate** the Software into your open-source projects.

**However, the GPLv3 is a "copyleft" license.** This means that if you distribute your application that uses this Software, your entire application must also be released under the GPLv3 or a compatible open-source license.

You can view the full legal text of the GPLv3 at: https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.html

